data.title: Kopecky Family Band - "Are You Listening"
data.meta_description: Second single from their debut album Kids Raising Kids. Received 6 AAA adds this week.
data.text:
Post by Devin on

Second single from their debut album Kids Raising Kids. Received 6 AAA adds this week.

Post by American Idiot on

I have no idea what the members of this band look like. Whenever I see the name of this band, I think of Tomas Kopecky playing in a band with his wife and kids jamming out. For those who don't know who Tomas Kopecky is, he's a hockey player on the Florida Panthers. The more you know...
